{"tid":464391,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"d 唐氏綜合症 既人成日都笑笑口，其實佢地係咪好開心？？","createTime":"2017-11-10T13:08:16.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-31T14:13:55.000Z","uid":123335,"like":304,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":86,"replies":[{"pid":"7548b631b804a9297473b2f834258ec501168d6a","tid":464391,"uid":123335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-10T13:08:16.000Z","msg":"出街見親唐氏綜合症既人<br />\n通常個個都笑笑口咁<br />\n唔知佢地其實係咪過得好開心？？<br />\n<br />\n利申：非歧視，我真係feel 到佢地內在快樂<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://a2.att.hudong.com/84/93/01300309316150141500939164254_s.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fa2.att.hudong.com%2F84%2F93%2F01300309316150141500939164254_s.jpg&h=72ba3488&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://rthk9.rthk.hk/special/rehab/images/cases/case07_04.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Frthk9.rthk.hk%2Fspecial%2Frehab%2Fimages%2Fcases%2Fcase07_04.jpg&h=b81ba101&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.bkmilk.com.hk/wp-content/uploads/2016/06/2016-06-15-Abortion1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.bkmilk.com.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2016%2F06%2F2016-06-15-Abortion1.jpg&h=06010930&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n有冇巴打知，唐氏綜合症既人係咪好易開心，好易滿足？<br />\n真係成日見佢地笑笑口<br />\n<br />\n會唔會普通正常人冇唐氏綜合症既人咁開心？<br />\n又要供樓 又要返工 俾老細鬧"},{"pid":"270d603ff6ebe1738760824ebdf7007384beeb4e","tid":464391,"uid":100150,"like":102,"dislike":859,"score":-757,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-10T13:09:04.000Z","msg":"見到自己個樣忍唔住笑出嚟"},{"pid":"c8f305adf1985c7876be18c923dc3a65e66b459c","tid":464391,"uid":54927,"like":274,"dislike":2,"score":272,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-10T13:09:11.000Z","msg":"有呢病人都簡單好多啦 有飯食 有野玩就得<br />\n普通人咁多負擔"},{"pid":"c8baa0a59491d862588b5c09047293143db7f6d3","tid":464391,"uid":44333,"like":42,"dislike":2,"score":40,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-10T13:13:33.000Z","msg":"好肯定話你知 係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a0a69188d37fd1a6001a709ee44d223c983cb4ef","tid":464391,"uid":102642,"like":70,"dislike":1,"score":69,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-10T13:16:19.000Z","msg":"無知是福"},{"pid":"78c9cfca1473cdd65898a905da334849ac89036d","tid":464391,"uid":56999,"like":22,"dislike":7,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-10T13:22:12.000Z","msg":"笑你on9咋"},{"pid":"ab2a971396c021843d41207e2b5baa3d82ec60fd","tid":464391,"uid":77092,"like":220,"dislike":1,"score":219,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-10T13:23:21.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f4b48e62fe87bb87df67e1e5c43d4af23369d260","tid":464391,"uid":94828,"like":106,"dislike":3,"score":103,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-10T13:23:40.000Z","msg":"諗返起你十歳前係點咪知"},{"pid":"95e44f0189f32bcd143ee9440140a4c374e6e790","tid":464391,"uid":25560,"like":112,"dislike":2,"score":110,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-10T13:34:14.000Z","msg":"會扭計同發脾氣<br />\n<br />\n利申：做義工帶過"},{"pid":"27d6fdadb580b7182f3fb979b6780379f9e935a5","tid":464391,"uid":93986,"like":4,"dislike":27,"score":-23,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-10T13:46:33.000Z","msg":"你當佢地係另一種外星人吧"},{"pid":"a8d61cae5fd02853bda33bb1ffe448b86d3ec324","tid":464391,"uid":103380,"like":1,"dislike":5,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-10T14:33:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ..."},{"pid":"fdb69718c20d777500e8a528634ddd2c2f3cf840","tid":464391,"uid":125509,"like":126,"dislike":2,"score":124,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-10T14:34:38.000Z","msg":"其實一個人 思想愈簡單 愈少野諗 就一定愈開心啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"944ee9e0d7fa1d3a77d63b946f9a50cd02f62440","tid":464391,"uid":24737,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-10T14:37:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>有呢病人都簡單好多啦 有飯食 有野玩就得<br />\n普通人咁多負擔</blockquote><br />\n湊佢果個辛苦呢</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e449b8a4387e2081656aaa4aa7d367082c7f0dd9","tid":464391,"uid":91330,"like":19,"dislike":52,"score":-33,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-10T14:42:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>見到自己個樣忍唔住笑出嚟</blockquote><br />\n好撚mean<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 落地獄啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a762dd7f8a4a2811e1b92293f563851834b49cf4","tid":464391,"uid":93890,"like":6,"dislike":6,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-10T21:20:11.000Z","msg":"口德-50"},{"pid":"7bd438b3359c30ea24166dfa342d7769bc3fa1b3","tid":464391,"uid":132088,"like":89,"dislike":15,"score":74,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-10T21:23:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>見到自己個樣忍唔住笑出嚟</blockquote><br />\n收嗲啦 屌你老母"},{"pid":"092c41d21e7b4ca28fcc193ea053c40bdb0863c4","tid":464391,"uid":124935,"like":89,"dislike":9,"score":80,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-10T21:42:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>見到自己個樣忍唔住笑出嚟</blockquote><br />\n屌你老母呀 你老母比狗屌呀"},{"pid":"1fc3ed108c6d6001a92e8c08c50a5b644af3baf2","tid":464391,"uid":79491,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-10T22:01:59.000Z","msg":"點解唐氏綜合症個個都差唔多樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 即使不同人種"},{"pid":"5041f8fab8f5af011de6b0cad7ee409901c78765","tid":464391,"uid":5303,"like":31,"dislike":1,"score":30,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-10T22:11:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>點解唐氏綜合症個個都差唔多樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 即使不同人種</blockquote><br />\n初認識唐氏綜合症人士的人會誤以為他們的樣子是倒模出來的，因為他們的外貌有一些相似的特徵，包括：頭扁、斜眼、扁鼻、口細、舌頭粗及有紋、肌肉張力差、手指短小、第一、二隻腳趾趾距較大、個子普遍較矮小及部份有痴肥傾向。當然，他們並非每種特徵也擁有，正如你我一樣，各人的外貌總會有分別的。<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.hk-dsa.org.hk/resources/ds/#chapter5\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk-dsa.org.hk%2Fresources%2Fds%2F%23chapter5&d=gXHq9wDoENUYm84wbPOUYYzu7PIJYhBZqlGrkalTKs4%3D&h=f1b6180e\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.hk-dsa.org.hk/resources/ds/#chapter5</a>"},{"pid":"d6cf96f9c5345c751787bf53aa42362f261a8b09","tid":464391,"uid":79491,"like":0,"dislike":12,"score":-12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-10T22:30:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>點解唐氏綜合症個個都差唔多樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 即使不同人種</blockquote><br />\n初認識唐氏綜合症人士的人會誤以為他們的樣子是倒模出來的，因為他們的外貌有一些相似的特徵，包括：頭扁、斜眼、扁鼻、口細、舌頭粗及有紋、肌肉張力差、手指短小、第一、二隻腳趾趾距較大、個子普遍較矮小及部份有痴肥傾向。當然，他們並非每種特徵也擁有，正如你我一樣，各人的外貌總會有分別的。<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.hk-dsa.org.hk/resources/ds/#chapter5\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk-dsa.org.hk%2Fresources%2Fds%2F%23chapter5&d=gXHq9wDoENUYm84wbPOUYYzu7PIJYhBZqlGrkalTKs4%3D&h=f1b6180e\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.hk-dsa.org.hk/resources/ds/#chapter5</a></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 長知識"},{"pid":"3719711ac281d7660b796f5dc2a04d98eeca0be8","tid":464391,"uid":3179,"like":4,"dislike":17,"score":-13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-10T23:12:25.000Z","msg":"應該係個病搞到佢地面部肌肉控制唔到<br />\n咀角向上揚起<br />\n正常人應該好難知道佢地內心世界<br />\n除非係精神科醫生"},{"pid":"2893f9da9da2b67a6a992fbd7905b3fea1d2cfac","tid":464391,"uid":37666,"like":56,"dislike":6,"score":50,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-10T23:22:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://tvmost.com.hk/most/uploads/images/2015/Article/2016.06/2016.06.28/light/02.3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftvmost.com.hk%2Fmost%2Fuploads%2Fimages%2F2015%2FArticle%2F2016.06%2F2016.06.28%2Flight%2F02.3.jpg&h=17316912&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"45791547cf1d8b5e501a742e56a490135bab27cf","tid":464391,"uid":63452,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-10T23:34:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>應該係個病搞到佢地面部肌肉控制唔到<br />\n咀角向上揚起<br />\n正常人應該好難知道佢地內心世界<br />\n除非係精神科醫生</blockquote><br />\n重有照顧佢地嘅carer，醫生都要問佢地平時係點，始終日對夜對"},{"pid":"4ad97e2