鳩佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 感覺好似想表示:望乜撚嘢四眼仔<br />\n個毒撚即刻托一托眼鏡望返張紙繼續點名好似乜事都無咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 個家長就罵個仔兩句<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n忍笑忍得好辛苦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"01e58fa76350882039634c7253cbe0f1c8b0444e","tid":464391,"uid":143816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-11T05:16:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>見到自己個樣忍唔住笑出嚟</blockquote><br />\n睇你個名同cm就知你係racist"},{"pid":"bda60dcc85f9581ed04e6c85aaee6c742aa17669","tid":464391,"uid":54597,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-11T06:14:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>佢地就日日返庇護工場入下筷子打份風流工,出面世界發生乜事都唔知,港獨建國又唔關佢地事,日日生活響自己世界<br />\n難為父母要照顧佢地一世<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n都無計。父母都控制唔到。<br />\n雖則話科技發達陀胎可以查。<br />\n但就當你查到。你都應該唔會忍心落<br />\n同埋你睇佢難為姐。<br />\n做老豆老母見到個仔女開心都好開心=)。</blockquote><br />\n其實好多都會選擇落"},{"pid":"ebd631c861bd5a567f476ca53ad1286b39b639e9","tid":464391,"uid":54597,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-11T06:34:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>唔係   我識一個好唔開心   <br />\n成日都會覺得自己係智障  能力低人一等而唔開心</blockquote><br />\n個樣正常？可能只係智商比較低但未去到智障</blockquote><br />\n唐氏個樣一定唔同<br />\n但不一定有嚴重智力問題<br />\n輕度果種最慘"},{"pid":"efd7b61b3bb00e5a8db3371d627fbcc4212f8c84","tid":464391,"uid":12269,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-11T08:38:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>平時笑霍金又得<br />\n笑唐氏綜合症就唔得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n成班若蓮喪子到呢......</blockquote><br />\n道德撚駁唔到?"},{"pid":"29550a0185e2c7892bb40954ca74037ec4047934","tid":464391,"uid":34571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-11T09:17:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>平時笑霍金又得<br />\n笑唐氏綜合症就唔得<img src=\"/assets/fac